rc=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f33f.png\" alt=\"🌿\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f30e.png\" alt=\"🌎\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Celebrate the diversity and resilience of New York State&#8217;s birds of prey through captivating stories and striking visuals. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4f7.png\" alt=\"📷\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Marvel at the unparalleled grace and power of raptors as we uncover their hidden world together. Join the flock! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f985.png\" alt=\"🦅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2764.png\" alt=\"❤\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-group-2-posts-to-generate-interest\">Group #2: Posts to Generate Interest</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Posts to generate interest serve as compelling invitations that pique curiosity and draw attention to our topic, product, or idea. Engaging posts have the power to captivate readers, evoke emotions, and leave a lasting impression.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Through generating interest, we create opportunities to build a dedicated following, foster brand loyalty, and ultimately convert curious readers into active participants and customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ideas for the “International Lovers of Brie Cheese” to Generate Interest</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Discover the lesser-known variations of brie cheese, from regional specialties to unique artisanal creations. Expand your cheese repertoire! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f30d.png\" alt=\"🌍\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Step into the role of a cheese connoisseur and embark on a journey of taste exploration with me. Let&#8217;s try unexpected pairings and share our findings! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9ea.png\" alt=\"🧪\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Unlock your inner chef and let&#8217;s dive into the kitchen to craft mouthwatering recipes featuring brie cheese. Get ready for some culinary adventures! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f373.png\" alt=\"🍳\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Explore the intricacies of brie cheese aging, from the optimal aging period to the impact on flavor development. Become an expert in cheese maturation! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/23f3.png\" alt=\"⏳\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Join me in unraveling the secrets of brie cheese selection and storage, ensuring that every bite delivers the perfect taste experience. Become a cheese-savvy aficionado! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5dd.png\" alt=\"🗝\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Elevate your cheese platter game with unique accompaniments that complement and enhance the flavors of brie cheese. Let&#8217;s create unforgettable tasting experiences! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f347.png\" alt=\"🍇\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Deepen your appreciation for the nuances of brie cheese as we explore the factors that influence its flavors, including terroir, milk source, and production techniques. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f331.png\" alt=\"🌱\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Unleash your inner artist by exploring the art of cheese carving and designing stunning presentations that celebrate the beauty of brie cheese. Let your creativity shine! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f3a8.png\" alt=\"🎨\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ideas for the “New York State Birds of Prey Fan Club” to Generate Interest</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Share tips on identifying different raptor species based on their unique physical characteristics. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f989.png\" alt=\"🦉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f50d.png\" alt=\"🔍\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Discuss the best locations and optimal times to spot various birds of prey in New York State. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f333.png\" alt=\"🌳\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f552.png\" alt=\"🕒\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Highlight the crucial role of citizen science in monitoring and protecting raptor populations. Be part of the conservation effort! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4ca.png\" alt=\"📊\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f33f.png\" alt=\"🌿\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Curate a list of must-read books and resources for anyone interested in learning more about New York&#8217;s birds of prey. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4da.png\" alt=\"📚\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f985.png\" alt=\"🦅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Debate the pros and cons of raptor rehabilitation and release programs. Join the conversation! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f3e5.png\" alt=\"🏥\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f504.png\" alt=\"🔄\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Challenge your birdwatching skills with fun raptor trivia and quizzes. How well do you know these majestic creatures? <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f914.png\" alt=\"🤔\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f3af.png\" alt=\"🎯\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Highlight the unique adaptations that allow raptors to excel as apex predators. Prepare to be amazed by nature&#8217;s engineering! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f31f.png\" alt=\"🌟\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f52c.png\" alt=\"🔬\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Discuss the impact of environmental factors, such as climate change, on the behavior and habitats of birds of prey. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f30d.png\" alt=\"🌍\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f321.png\" alt=\"🌡\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Showcase the captivating aerial acrobatics of raptors through stunning photographs and videos. Prepare to be mesmerized! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4f8.png\" alt=\"📸\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2728.png\" alt=\"✨\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Engage your imagination by sharing fascinating folklore and mythologies surrounding birds of prey. Let your creativity soar! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1fab6.png\" alt=\"🪶\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2728.png\" alt=\"✨\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-group-3-posts-to-generate-desire\">Group #3: Posts to Generate Desire</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>These posts tap into the aspirations, needs, and wants of our audience, igniting a longing for what we offer. By crafting persuasive and emotionally resonant content, we create a sense of urgency and exclusivity that compels readers to take action.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ideas for the “International Lovers of Brie Cheese” to Generate Desire</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Ready to take your love for brie cheese to the next level? Join our exclusive International Lovers of Brie Cheese community and connect with fellow enthusiasts worldwide! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f310.png\" alt=\"🌐\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Become a part of the thriving brie cheese community, where you can engage in insightful discussions, share experiences, and learn from seasoned experts. Let&#8217;s grow together! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4bc.png\" alt=\"💼\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Unlock a treasure trove of premium content, including masterclasses, interviews with cheese artisans, and insider tips you won&#8217;t find anywhere else. Join the inner circle! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5dd.png\" alt=\"🗝\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4da.png\" alt=\"📚\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gain access to members-only events, virtual tastings, and exclusive cheese-related experiences that will delight your senses and elevate your passion for brie cheese! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f377.png\" alt=\"🍷\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>As a valued member, you&#8217;ll enjoy special bonuses like early access to new cheese releases, discounts on cheese-related products, and more. Don&#8217;t miss out! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f381.png\" alt=\"🎁\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4ab.png\" alt=\"💫\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Build meaningful connections with fellow brie cheese enthusiasts, including chefs, sommeliers, and food bloggers. Expand your network and share your love for cheese! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f91d.png\" alt=\"🤝\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9c0.png\" alt=\"🧀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Join a supportive and vibrant community of like-minded individuals who share your love for all things brie cheese. Together, we&#8217;ll celebrate the joys of gastronomy! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f32e.png\" alt=\"🌮\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ideas for the “New York State Birds of Prey Fan Club” to Generate Desire</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Invite you to join the New York State Birds of Prey Fan Club and unlock exclusive access to a vibrant community of bird enthusiasts. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f985.png\" alt=\"🦅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f31f.png\" alt=\"🌟\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Introduce our monthly virtual meetups where members share their birdwatching experiences and learn from each other. Join the conversation! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5d3.png\" alt=\"🗓\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4ac.png\" alt=\"💬\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Offer a sneak peek into our extensive database of raptor sightings, available exclusively to club members. Ready to become an expert spotter? <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4ca.png\" alt=\"📊\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/social-media-ai-pmpro.jpg\" alt=\"Info-graphic for Example Social Media Topic Ideas\" class=\"wp-image-514327\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/social-media-ai-pmpro.jpg 1600w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/social-media-ai-pmpro-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/social-media-ai-pmpro-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/social-media-ai-pmpro-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/social-media-ai-pmpro-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/social-media-ai-pmpro-128x72.jpg 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-be-the-human-behind-the-ai\">Be The Human Behind the AI</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While AI like ChatGPT can be an invaluable tool for generating post ideas and aiding content creation, it&#8217;s crucial to remember that <strong>the most compelling and engaging social media posts will always have a human touch.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your unique perspective, passion, and authenticity are what truly resonate with your audience and make your content stand out.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When choosing a platform, remember that it&#8217;s not about<em> being on every platform</em> but <em>being on the right platforms for your audience and your goals</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you grow and learn more about your audience, don&#8217;t be afraid to reassess and adjust your strategy as needed. After all, flexibility is a key aspect of successful social media marketing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Always consider your personal preferences, the style of content you enjoy creating, and the type of interaction you want to have with your audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in all, when you combine the power of AI with this approach, you’ll be well on your way to generating compelling social media posts that effectively engage your audience and support your growth goals.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"WordPress Post Visibility: Password Protection vs. Membership Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:103:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wordpress-post-visibility-password-protection-vs-membership-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 28 Aug 2023 14:00:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"General\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/?p=513426\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:510:\"WordPress offers several features to control the visibility of blog content. Two commonly used methods are password protection and membership plugins. In this how-to post, we explore core WordPress post visibility features and compare them to using a membership plugin with free or paid user registration to restrict access to exclusive member content. WordPress Core <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wordpress-post-visibility-password-protection-vs-membership-plugins/\" rel=\"nofollow\">(more...)</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"PMPro Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18750:\"\n<p>WordPress offers several features to control the visibility of blog content. Two commonly used methods are password protection and membership plugins.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this how-to post, we explore core WordPress post visibility features and compare them to using a membership plugin with free or paid user registration to restrict access to exclusive member content.</p>\n\n\n\n<img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"852\" height=\"479\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-password-protection-2-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"Banner Image for WordPress Post Visibility\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-password-protection-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-password-protection-2-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-password-protection-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-password-protection-2-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-password-protection-2-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-password-protection-2.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 852px) 100vw, 852px\" />\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-grey-blue-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-yoast-seo-table-of-contents yoast-table-of-contents\"><h2>Table of contents</h2><ul><li><a href=\"#h-wordpress-core-feature\" data-level=\"2\">WordPress Core Feature: Setting a Post as Password Protected</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-membership-plugins-restricted-content\" data-level=\"2\">Using Membership Plugins for Restricted Content Access</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-video\" data-level=\"2\">Video: WordPress Password Protected Posts or a Membership Plugin: What&#8217;s Right for You?</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-how-to-password-protect-post\" data-level=\"2\">How to Password Protect a Post in WordPress</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-how-to-use-membership-plugin-post-visibility\" data-level=\"2\">How to Use a Membership Plugin for WordPress Post Visibility</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-choosing-post-visibility-method\" data-level=\"2\">Choosing a WordPress Post Visibility Method: Passwords or Memberships?</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-wordpress-core-feature\">WordPress Core Feature: Setting a Post as Password Protected</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Password protecting a post is a <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/content-visibility-block-editor/#password-protected-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">built-in feature in WordPress</a>, allowing you to control who can access specific content on your website. When you edit a post or page, you can find the post visibility settings under the &#8220;Publish&#8221; option at the top-right corner of the edit screen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, all posts and pages are set to &#8220;Public,&#8221; making them visible to everyone upon publication. However, you can change the visibility to &#8220;Password Protected,&#8221; and then set a password of your choice for that particular post or page. Once set, visitors attempting to view the content will be prompted to enter the password before gaining access.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pros of Password Protected Content</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>No Additional Plugins:</strong> This feature is available natively in WordPress, eliminating the need for additional plugins.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Simple Setup:</strong> Password protection is easy to set up and requires no technical expertise.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Quick Access:</strong> Users can access the protected content immediately after entering the password.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cons of Password Protected Content</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Limited User Data:</strong> Password protection does not collect user information beyond the password itself. You have no idea who accessed your post, or who has shared the password.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Manual Sharing:</strong> Administrators must manually share the password with intended users, which can be cumbersome for larger memberships.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/post-as-password-protected-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Infographic of pros and cons of setting a post as password protected\" class=\"wp-image-513430\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/post-as-password-protected-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/post-as-password-protected-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/post-as-password-protected-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/post-as-password-protected-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/post-as-password-protected-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/post-as-password-protected.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-membership-plugins-restricted-content\">Using Membership Plugins for Restricted Content Access</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, website owners can opt for membership plugins like Paid Memberships Pro, which offer a more robust solution for restricting access to specific content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a membership plugin, admins can create free or paid membership levels and collect user data during the registration process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Membership plugins provide various features, such as user management, payment integration, and content restriction rules. In contrast to password protection, users sign up for memberships, granting them access to exclusive content based on their membership level.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pros of Using Membership Plugins</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Enhanced User Data:</strong> Membership plugins collect user information, providing insights into your audience.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tiered Access:</strong> Offer different membership levels with varying content access for a more flexible approach.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Streamlined Access:</strong> Members can log in to access content without entering passwords for each protected post.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cons of Using Membership Plugins</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Learning Curve:</strong> Setting up membership plugins may require more time and technical knowledge.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Additional Plugins:</strong> Installing and managing a membership plugin adds a small amount of complexity to your website.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/membership-plugins-restricted-access-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Infographic for Pros and Cons on Using Membership Plugins for Restricted Content Access\" class=\"wp-image-513434\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/membership-plugins-restricted-access-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/membership-plugins-restricted-access-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/membership-plugins-restricted-access-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/membership-plugins-restricted-access-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/membership-plugins-restricted-access-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/membership-plugins-restricted-access.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-video\">Video: WordPress Password Protected Posts or a Membership Plugin: What&#8217;s Right for You?</h2>\n\n\n\n<center><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3kIMk4Yw3I8\" width=\"805\" height=\"453\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></center>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-how-to-password-protect-post\">How to Password Protect a Post in WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Log in to your WordPress Dashboard.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Navigate to the <strong>Posts</strong> section on the left sidebar and <strong>select the post you want to protect</strong> with a password.\n<ol>\n<li>If you want to protect a page instead, follow the same steps but navigate to <strong>Pages</strong> instead of Posts.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>On the post editor screen, locate the <strong>Publish</strong> panel on the right-hand side.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Under <strong>Visibility</strong>, click on the Edit link next to Public.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-post-visibility-1024x422.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of WP post settings - set visibility \" class=\"wp-image-513438\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-post-visibility-1024x422.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-post-visibility-300x124.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-post-visibility-1170x482.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-post-visibility.jpg 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Choose the <strong>Password Protected</strong> option from the expanded visibility options. A text box will appear below the Password Protected option.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"526\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-password-on-post-1024x526.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of WordPress settings to set password\" class=\"wp-image-513439\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-password-on-post-1024x526.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-password-on-post-300x154.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-password-on-post-1170x601.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-set-password-on-post.jpg 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li><strong>Enter the desired password</strong> for the post in this box.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Update or publish</strong> the post to apply the changes.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, when visitors try to access the password-protected post, they will be prompted to enter the password to view the content.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"662\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-password-protected-post-1024x662.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of password protected WP post\" class=\"wp-image-513440\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-password-protected-post-1024x662.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-password-protected-post-300x194.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-password-protected-post-1170x757.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wordpress-password-protected-post.jpg 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-how-to-use-membership-plugin-post-visibility\">How to Use a Membership Plugin for WordPress Post Visibility</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Log in to your WordPress Dashboard.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Go to <strong>Plugins</strong> on the left sidebar and click on <strong>Add New</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>In the search bar, type <strong>Paid Memberships Pro</strong> and click the Install Now button next to the plugin.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Once installed, click <strong>Activate</strong> to activate the plugin.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A setup wizard will appear to <strong>guide you through the initial setup</strong>. Follow the instructions and provide necessary details about your membership site. You can choose to set up a free membership level for this example.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>After completing the setup wizard, <strong>navigate back to the post</strong> you want to restrict access to.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scroll down to the new <strong>Require Membership</strong> panel, which is added by the PMPro plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-set-membership-required-for-post-1024x523.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of post edit page showing require membership panel settings\" class=\"wp-image-513441\" style=\"width:805px;height:411px\" width=\"805\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-set-membership-required-for-post-1024x523.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-set-membership-required-for-post-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-set-membership-required-for-post-1170x598.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-set-membership-required-for-post.jpg 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 805px) 100vw, 805px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>Check the box next to the membership level you want <strong>to grant access to this post</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"554\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-select-memberships-levels-for-post-1024x554.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of WP post edit page selecting which membership levels are required to view post\" class=\"wp-image-513442\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-select-memberships-levels-for-post-1024x554.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-select-memberships-levels-for-post-300x162.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-select-memberships-levels-for-post-1170x633.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-select-memberships-levels-for-post.jpg 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li><strong>Save or update the post</strong> to apply the membership restriction.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, when users visit the post, they will see a teaser of the content, along with a prompt to register for membership to access the full post.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-69 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"574\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-no-access-to-members-only-post-1024x574.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of frontend restrict content with membership plugin\" class=\"wp-image-513443\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-no-access-to-members-only-post-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-no-access-to-members-only-post-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-no-access-to-members-only-post-1170x656.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-no-access-to-members-only-post-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-no-access-to-members-only-post.jpg 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"624\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-complete-checkout-to-view-post-1024x624.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of membership checkout to gain access to restricted content\" class=\"wp-image-513444\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-complete-checkout-to-view-post-1024x624.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-complete-checkout-to-view-post-300x183.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-complete-checkout-to-view-post-1170x713.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-complete-checkout-to-view-post.jpg 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-alert-message is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>Note: you do not need to set a post password or adjust visibility settings when using a membership plugin like PMPro.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-choosing-post-visibility-method\">Choosing a WordPress Post Visibility Method: Passwords or Memberships?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Both password protection and membership plugins offer a solution for restricting access to content on WordPress websites.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Password protection is a quick and easy way to start providing members-only content, but it lacks the comprehensive features and user data collection provided by membership plugins.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you need a simple and straightforward approach, password protection may suffice initially.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you are looking for a more intuitive way to manage memberships, user data, and content access, investing in a reputable membership plugin like Paid Memberships Pro could be a more suitable long-term solution for your WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Browse the <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/features/\">features of PMPro</a> or <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/pricing/\">view our plans</a> (starting at $0) to get started today.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Evaluate your needs and goals to make an informed decision on which method aligns best with your content protection strategy.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"Paid Memberships Pro vs. Memberful\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/pmpro-vs-memberful/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 21 Aug 2023 14:00:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Product Comparison\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/?p=512353\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:455:\"Imagine yourself at a crossroads. One sign reads “Paid Memberships Pro.&#8221; The other “Memberful.” Both seem like good options for building your membership site, but you want to pick only the best path forward. Which one do you choose—PMPro vs. Memberful?&#160; Choosing a membership platform is a common concern among business owners starting out in <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/pmpro-vs-memberful/\" rel=\"nofollow\">(more...)</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"PMPro Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20815:\"\n<p>Imagine yourself at a crossroads. One sign reads “Paid Memberships Pro.&#8221; The other “Memberful.” Both seem like good options for building your membership site, but you want to pick only the best path forward. Which one do you choose—PMPro vs. Memberful?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing a membership platform is a common concern among business owners starting out in the memberships space. After all, <a href=\"https://www.gartner.com/smarterwithgartner/top-10-trends-in-digital-commerce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">75% of online</a> businesses want to offer memberships to their customers, and you want to get the backend right the first time.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#8217;t sweat it. We&#8217;re here to clear the fog and help you make an informed choice. In this post, we’ll compare two popular membership plugins — Paid Memberships Pro vs. Memberful — so you can make an informed decision.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"852\" height=\"479\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/mem-vs-pmpro-1-1-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"Banner Image for PMPro vs Memberful\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/mem-vs-pmpro-1-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/mem-vs-pmpro-1-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/mem-vs-pmpro-1-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/mem-vs-pmpro-1-1-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/mem-vs-pmpro-1-1-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/mem-vs-pmpro-1-1.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 852px) 100vw, 852px\" />\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-grey-blue-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-yoast-seo-table-of-contents yoast-table-of-contents\"><h2>Table of contents</h2><ul><li><a href=\"#h-paid-memberships-pro\" data-level=\"2\">Paid Memberships Pro</a><ul><li><a href=\"#h-key-membership-features-of-pmpro\" data-level=\"3\">Key Membership Features of PMPro</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-administrative-features-of-pmpro\" data-level=\"3\">Administrative Features of PMPro</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-user-experience-in-paid-memberships-pro\" data-level=\"3\">User Experience in Paid Memberships Pro</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-paid-memberships-pro-price-points\" data-level=\"3\">Paid Memberships Pro Price Points</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#h-memberful\" data-level=\"2\">Memberful</a><ul><li><a href=\"#h-key-features-of-memberful\" data-level=\"3\">Key Features of Memberful</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-user-experience-in-memberful\" data-level=\"3\">User Experience in Memberful</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-memberful-price-points\" data-level=\"3\">Memberful Price Points</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#h-pmpro-vs-memberful\" data-level=\"2\">PMPro vs. Memberful</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-why-choose-paid-memberships-pro\" data-level=\"2\">Why Choose Paid Memberships Pro?</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-grow-your-membership-with-paid-memberships-pro\" data-level=\"2\">Grow Your Membership with Paid Memberships Pro</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-paid-memberships-pro\">Paid Memberships Pro</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Paid Memberships Pro is a robust and modern WordPress membership plugin. Because it’s a plugin, it integrates seamlessly with your existing WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s designed to easily handle membership needs, making it a popular choice for associations and nonprofit organizations, blogs and news organizations, communities, courses and coaching, paid newsletters, and more. PMPro works perfectly, even for less tech-savvy users, so you can start your membership site with minimal effort.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-key-membership-features-of-pmpro\">Key Membership Features of PMPro</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Content Restrictions: </strong>You can restrict unlimited content, create personalized content for each member, and drip content over time to improve engagement.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Payment Options</strong>: Integrates with popular <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/gateway/\">payment gateways</a> like Stripe, PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Wallet. PMPro allows you to process recurring payments, create flexible pricing, offer trials, introductory, or front-loaded pricing, and even refund payments right from your WordPress dashboard.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>User Control</strong>: Your members and subscribers can manage their profiles, view their membership status and invoices, change their payment methods, or cancel their membership at any time without reaching support.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-administrative-features-of-pmpro\">Administrative Features of PMPro</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Member Management</strong>: Paid Memberships Pro enables you to create unlimited membership tiers with free, one-time payment, or a recurring subscription such as annual, monthly, weekly, daily, or hourly charges, depending on your needs. To manage the various types of memberships you offer, you can customize registration and profile forms with <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/documentation/user-fields/\">User Fields</a> to distinguish who signs up for what type of membership.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Free Service: </strong>PMPro is free with the option to upgrade to paid plans that allow you to add premium Add Ons, read in-depth tutorials to customize your membership, and access our premium technical support for members only. But you can do key functions, like <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/pmpro-zapier/\">integrating with Zapier</a>, as part of the free core.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Admin Reports: </strong>PMPro includes multiple detailed reports, including sales and revenue, signups and cancellations, active members by level, as well as data for member visits, views, and logins.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Scalability</strong>: The core plugin is free and comes packed with features, making it a cost-effective solution for those just starting. There are no limits on the number of members, types of content you can protect, or levels you can offer in the core version. However, there is an option to upgrade if you need premium Add Ons or greater support.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: PMPro offers basic free support via the WordPress.org support area. Premium members gain access to advanced technical support and plus hundreds of tutorials for advanced customization. The support team works closely with our developers to quickly resolve issues or create code patches.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/key-features-pmpro.jpg\" alt=\"Infographic of Key Features of Paid Memberships Pro\" class=\"wp-image-512363\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/key-features-pmpro.jpg 1600w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/key-features-pmpro-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/key-features-pmpro-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/key-features-pmpro-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/key-features-pmpro-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/key-features-pmpro-128x72.jpg 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-user-experience-in-paid-memberships-pro\">User Experience in Paid Memberships Pro</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>PMPro offers an excellent user experience. For admins, you have a simple yet comprehensive interface that displays all the essential settings, like member management, order history, content protections, activity statistics, and more, right on your WordPress dashboard.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with a powerful admin dashboard, PMPro also gives your members control of their memberships. Your members can manage their profiles from the site&#8217;s front end and do things like:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Reset their passwords</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Manage their profiles with custom user fields</li>\n\n\n\n<li>View their membership status and invoices</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Change their payment methods</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Upgrade or cancel their membership</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>By giving members the power to make basic changes on their own, you can reduce admin responsibilities. Who doesn&#8217;t love saving support time with fewer mundane tasks.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-paid-memberships-pro-price-points\">Paid Memberships Pro Price Points</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Paid Memberships Pro’s plugin is free to download and install. The plugin includes <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-on-category/free/\">33 free Add Ons</a>. It offers everything you need to launch and build your membership, including unlimited restricted content, unlimited membership levels and members. You can offer free or paid subscriptions through built-in integration with Stripe, PayPal Express, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As your online business grows, you may want features beyond what&#8217;s in the standard plugin. PMPro supports those needs, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-pmpro-offers-three-pricing-plans\">PMPro Offers Three Pricing Plans</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Standard</strong>: Priced at $247 per year, the Standard plan adds premium support, advanced code recipes, automatic updates. There are 20 Standard Add Ons included in this tier for a single production site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Plus</strong>: The Plus plan is priced at $397 per year and is best for building advanced membership sites. It includes everything in the Standard plan plus 29 Plus Add Ons for up to two production sites.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Builder</strong>: The Builder plan costs $697 per year and is best for agencies or devs who run multiple sites. It includes everything in the Plus plan for up to five production sites.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-pricing-table.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of PMPro Pricing Table\" class=\"wp-image-512365\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-pricing-table.jpg 1600w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-pricing-table-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-pricing-table-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-pricing-table-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-pricing-table-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-pricing-table-128x72.jpg 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-memberful\">Memberful</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Memberful is a hosted member database that caters to a wide range of membership needs. It’s designed to work well for any type of content and offers various monetization options. Memberful doesn’t require a WordPress site. Instead, you can use Memberful with their website builder and add checkout buttons to your existing website. This may seem somewhat disconnected, but it&#8217;s the only path they offer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-key-features-of-memberful\">Key Features of Memberful</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Easy Setup</strong>: Memberful is easy to use with a focus on the basics so you can set up your plans.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Flexible Subscription Plans</strong>: With Memberful, you can create any kind of subscription plan that makes the most sense for your audience. It supports a monthly, annual, weekly, quarterly, fixed number of times, and more.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Full Control</strong>: Memberful gives you full control of your membership site if you use their website builder. It offers a visual editor, allows you to add custom fields to collect information, and lets you personalize the account emails sent to your members. This level of control is only accessible with the website builder, not if you incorporate the platform into an existing site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Member Management</strong>: Memberful provides the tools to manage subscriptions, process refunds, create staff accounts with targeted permissions, add private notes, and monitor integration status.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/memberful-pmpro.jpg\" alt=\"Infographic of Key Features of Memberful\" class=\"wp-image-512389\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/memberful-pmpro.jpg 1600w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/memberful-pmpro-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/memberful-pmpro-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/memberful-pmpro-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/memberful-pmpro-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/memberful-pmpro-128x72.jpg 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-user-experience-in-memberful\">User Experience in Memberful</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With Memberful, members manage their accounts outside the WordPress site, within Memberful’s app. Members can then access their content, manage their subscriptions, and access their account through this external interface.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-memberful-price-points\">Memberful Price Points</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Pro Plan, at $25 per month with a 4.9% transaction fee. It provides unlimited membership levels, all integrations, and additional features like group subscriptions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Premium Plan, costing $100 per month, with a 4.9% transaction fee, includes all Pro Plan features.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All plans offer unlimited members and backups.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-site-navigation-background-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left\" id=\"h-pmpro-vs-memberful\">PMPro vs. Memberful</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Want to see how Paid Memberships Pro and Memberful stack up? Check out this table that compares the two membership-building options.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table alignwide is-style-stripes\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>Feature</strong></th><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><strong>Paid Memberships Pro</strong></th><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><strong>Memberful</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Cost</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">$0 &#8211; $697/year</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Starts at $25/month (Pro) + 4.9% transaction fee</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Customization</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Multiple membership tiers, customizable membership trial periods, customizable membership renewal dates, custom member homepages</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Content restriction, unlimited membership levels, basic member emails, member dashboard</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Data and Reporting</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Sales and revenue, signups and cancellations, member visits and logins, order management</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Reporting by time</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Integrations</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">WooCommerce, Mailchimp, Zapier, Social Login, BuddyBoss, bbPress, Zapier, Social Login, Events Manager, The Events Calendar, All-in-One Event Calendar. <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-on-category/integration/\">View all 55 integrations</a></td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Available with Pro and Premium plans. Stripe, PayPal, MailChimp, ConvertKit, Zapier</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Administrative Tools</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Manually add members, import and export members, assign a membership manager, tax handling</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">CSV user import, member management dashboard</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Content Restriction</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Built-in content restrictions for many types of content</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Built-in content restrictions</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Payment Gateways</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Stripe, PayPal, and more. All built-in gateways and gateway plugins we develop are free. <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/gateway/\">View all gateways</a></td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Only supports Stripe</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">User Experience</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Members can manage their profiles, view their memberships and invoices, login and reset their passwords on the front end of your site, change their payment methods, and update or cancel their memberships.</td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Members can manage their profiles, view their memberships and invoices, login and reset their passwords on the front end of your site, change their payment methods, and update or cancel their memberships.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-why-choose-paid-memberships-pro\">Why Choose Paid Memberships Pro?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want a membership plugin that puts your members at the heart of everything? Look no further than Paid Memberships Pro.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We comparing PMPro vs. Memberful, it&#8217;s clear that PMPro focuses on providing a seamless and enriching experience for admins <em>and</em> members. PMPro makes it easier for you to engage, upsell, and maintain a strong relationship with your community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike other membership plugins, PMPro offers a high level of flexibility and customization. No matter the feature you need to handle your memberships, PMPro has you covered. And since PMPro is free, you can easily launch and grow your membership without paying fees each time you scale.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In fact, PMPro is 100% free. If you decide to pay for one of our premium plans, you will pay a flat fee that doesn’t change. Unlike Memberful, your growth is not taxed based on the size of your community. This feature makes PMPro a great solution if you plan for your community to get bigger.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, we don’t take any part of your revenue at the platform level. The only fees you have to worry about are those associated with your payment gateway.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, with its advanced data and reporting, you have everything you need to monitor and optimize your membership business for success.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But it&#8217;s not just about the features. PMPro empowers you to build and grow your online community with full control and flexibility from your current WordPress website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-grow-your-membership-with-paid-memberships-pro\">Grow Your Membership with Paid Memberships Pro</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make the process of creating your membership site simple. As the most robust membership plugin for WordPress, PMPro provides everything you need to run a successful online business. Aside from the plugin itself, PMPro also offers in-depth support, live events, and the confidence that you fully own your platform and data.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you&#8217;re ready to take your online community to the next level, <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/pricing/\">try PMPro</a>. It’s the partner you need to build an engaged business.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"How an Online Yoga School Grew by 1,000% on a Membership Model With Paid Memberships Pro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/yoga-school-grew-pmpro/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 18 Aug 2023 12:09:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Membership Site Case Studies\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Use Case: Courses\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:1