 put her yoga business online. In 2012 she hosted her first online Vinyasa yoga class for beginners. Under the name Monkey Yoga (La Scimmia means “monkey” in Italian), she sold lessons and video––but without a membership component.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, without the recurring revenue, automation, and scalability provided by a membership model, Sara did not have the time or resources to dedicate to growing her online yoga school business the way she wanted. This changed with Paid Memberships Pro.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-site-navigation-background-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-76 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:80%\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-plain\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-73 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<p class=\"has-luminous-vivid-amber-color has-text-color\"><i class=\"fa  fa-star\"></i> <i class=\"fa  fa-star\"></i> <i class=\"fa  fa-star\"></i> <i class=\"fa  fa-star\"></i> <i class=\"fa  fa-star\"></i></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Having a membership based business means recurring revenue, automation, scalability and, so important for our business, <strong>a premium paid community.</strong></p>\n</div>\n<cite>—Sara Bigatti, La Scimmia Yoga</cite></blockquote>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:20%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-thumbnail has-custom-border is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"Sara Bigatti\" class=\"wp-image-482134\" style=\"border-radius:9999px\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-80x80.jpeg 80w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti.jpeg 488w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"852\" height=\"479\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/yoga-school-pmpro-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"Banner Image for Case Study, La Scimmia Yoga\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/yoga-school-pmpro-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/yoga-school-pmpro-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/yoga-school-pmpro-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/yoga-school-pmpro-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/yoga-school-pmpro-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/yoga-school-pmpro.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 852px) 100vw, 852px\" />\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-grey-blue-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-yoast-seo-table-of-contents yoast-table-of-contents\"><h2>Table of contents</h2><ul><li><a href=\"#h-why-paid-memberships-pro-for-an-online-yoga-school\" data-level=\"2\">Why Paid Memberships Pro For an Online Yoga School</a><ul><li><a href=\"#h-1-optimized-for-wordpress-integration\" data-level=\"3\">1. Optimized for WordPress Integration</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-2-all-the-necessary-back-end-business-tools\" data-level=\"3\">2. All the Necessary Back-End Business Tools</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-3-easy-customer-side-processes-that-facilitate-conversion\" data-level=\"3\">3. Easy Customer-Side Processes that Facilitate Conversion</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-4-excellent-tech-support\" data-level=\"3\">4. Excellent Tech Support</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#h-how-paid-memberships-pro-made-a-difference\" data-level=\"2\">How Paid Memberships Pro Made a Difference</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-moving-forward\" data-level=\"2\">Moving Forward</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-la-scimmia-yoga-tech-stack\" data-level=\"2\">La Scimmia Yoga Tech Stack</a></li><li><a href=\"#h-where-to-find-la-scimmia-yoga-online\" data-level=\"2\">Where to Find La Scimmia Yoga Online</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-why-paid-memberships-pro-for-an-online-yoga-school\">Why Paid Memberships Pro For an Online Yoga School</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-1-optimized-for-wordpress-integration\">1. Optimized for WordPress Integration</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sara was already using WordPress for her yoga course website. Her technical advisor and developer Mirco, an experienced WordPress developer, had tinkered with Paid Memberships Pro years earlier, but had never yet had the opportunity to deploy it on a live site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With his expertise, he and Sara found it was the WordPress integrated tool they needed to create and support a powerful, growing online yoga school.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-2-all-the-necessary-back-end-business-tools\">2. All the Necessary Back-End Business Tools</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The advantages of using PMPro for an online yoga school, besides integrating seamlessly with WordPress, were many. With most of her target audience residing in Italy, a detailed and finely-tuned set-up was necessary to address the complexity of taxes, invoicing, and multiple gateways.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-3-easy-customer-side-processes-that-facilitate-conversion\">3. Easy Customer-Side Processes that Facilitate Conversion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On the front-end, site visitors find an easy subscription process to get into the platform, with no extraneous or unnecessary steps. PMPro is robust enough to withstand the traffic peaks the site gets at certain times of the day, so the site is always available.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"604\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-new-1024x604.png\" alt=\"An example image of new courses on the La Scimmia web site\" class=\"wp-image-513664\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-new-1024x604.png 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-new-300x177.png 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-new-1536x906.png 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-new-2048x1207.png 2048w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-new-1170x690.png 1170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Similarly, a highly customizable, easy-to-use one-page checkout process helps to convert customers. A PMPro Add On, <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/subscription-delays/\">Subscription Delays</a>, also allows visitors to test the course and community before committing to payment.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-4-excellent-tech-support\">4. Excellent Tech Support</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sara notes that any snags they may have run into during set-up were easily resolved with “top-level” assistance from PMPro’s staff and support team.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-advantages-la-scimmia.jpg\" alt=\"Info-graphic of Paid Memberships Pro\'s advantages\" class=\"wp-image-513630\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-advantages-la-scimmia.jpg 1600w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-advantages-la-scimmia-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-advantages-la-scimmia-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-advantages-la-scimmia-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-advantages-la-scimmia-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pmpro-advantages-la-scimmia-128x72.jpg 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Sara does have a wishlist for her online yoga school and for Paid Memberships Pro, and is hoping to see more flexibility around multi-currency, as well as invoices and return documents optimized for the EU.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nevertheless, she is enthusiastic about PMPro’s advantages, citing its:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Flexibility</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Extendability</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scalability</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Smooth Processes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Top Level Paid Support</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Supportive Community</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70)\">\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-borders-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-borders-background-color has-background is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-80 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:80%\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-plain\">\n<p>It’s simple, powerful and supportive when trying to implement our next crazy idea.</p>\n<cite>—Sara Bigatti, La Scimmia Yoga</cite></blockquote>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:20%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-thumbnail has-custom-border is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"Sara Bigatti\" class=\"wp-image-482134\" style=\"border-radius:9999px\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-80x80.jpeg 80w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti.jpeg 488w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-borders-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-borders-background-color has-background is-style-wide\"/>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-grey-blue-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-how-paid-memberships-pro-made-a-difference\">How Paid Memberships Pro Made a Difference</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-85 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-82 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-dark-blue-color has-text-color has-poppins-font-family\"><i class=\"fa  fa-arrow-up-right-dots\"></i> <strong>Membership Growth Times Ten</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>With the switch to Paid Memberships Pro, Sara now offers monthly and yearly memberships in her online yoga school, <em>resulting in a customer base ten times the number</em> she had enrolled previously.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-83 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-dark-blue-color has-text-color has-poppins-font-family\"><i class=\"fa  fa-user-plus\"></i> <strong>Most Not-Yet-Committed Visitors Become Members</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, thanks to the Subscription Delays Add On, which allows users to give the course a trial run before committing to paying, <em>two-thirds of all trial customers become paid members</em>.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-84 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-dark-blue-color has-text-color has-poppins-font-family\"><i class=\"fa  fa-clock\"></i> <strong>Time to Focus on Business Growth and Keeping Members Engaged</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The automation and scalability of the premium paid community allows Sara to focus on growing her business and adding new features and services.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-borders-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-borders-background-color has-background is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Sara adds new courses to her online yoga school at least once a month or more, creating a momentum that keeps her paid community excited, enthusiastic, and motivated.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Without the freedom and extra time PMPro gives Sara via recurring revenue and automation, this would be difficult to do.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"591\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-1024x591.png\" alt=\"An example image of the La Scimmia courses\" class=\"wp-image-513668\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-1024x591.png 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-300x173.png 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-1536x887.png 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-2048x1183.png 2048w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-courses-1170x676.png 1170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70)\">\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-borders-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-borders-background-color has-background is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-89 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:20%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-thumbnail has-custom-border is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"Sara Bigatti\" class=\"wp-image-482134\" style=\"border-radius:9999px\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti-80x80.jpeg 80w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pmpro-reviewer-sara-bigatti.jpeg 488w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:80%\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-plain\">\n<p>We offer monthly and annual memberships to our customers. Our customer base has grown 10x thanks to the membership-based model and the versatility of PMPro.</p>\n<cite>—Sara Bigatti, La Scimmia Yoga</cite></blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-borders-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-borders-background-color has-background is-style-wide\"/>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"561\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-member-profile-1024x561.png\" alt=\"Screenshot of Member Profile page in La Simmia Yoga online school\" class=\"wp-image-513665\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-member-profile-1024x561.png 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-member-profile-300x164.png 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-member-profile-1536x842.png 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-member-profile-2048x1123.png 2048w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/la-simmia-member-profile-1170x642.png 1170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-moving-forward\">Moving Forward</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Currently, Sara uses ads and promotes her courses by sharing content on various social networks, including free lessons on her <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/lascimmiayoga/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">YouTube channel</a>, and interviews and advice on <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/33fHhfSIXyT2tXX8XxW9vA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spotify</a>. While attracting new members is not easy, she is looking to grow La Scimmia Yoga to twice its current membership within the next two years. Adding more features that will enhance community growth is in the plans as well, and eventually, she hopes to move the community from the social networks entirely to the platform.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-box-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saras-words-of-advice-pmpro.jpg\" alt=\"Info-graphic for Sara\'s Words of Advice\" class=\"wp-image-513640\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saras-words-of-advice-pmpro.jpg 1600w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saras-words-of-advice-pmpro-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saras-words-of-advice-pmpro-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saras-words-of-advice-pmpro-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saras-words-of-advice-pmpro-1170x658.jpg 1170w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saras-words-of-advice-pmpro-128x72.jpg 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sara shares some words of advice and encouragement for anyone considering starting a membership-driven website:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Offer powerful, premium content</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Use video</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Do use your face to create personal connection and invite communication</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keep your platform constantly growing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Listen to your audience</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Be community-driven</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70)\">\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-borders-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-borders-background-color has-background is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-93 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:80%\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-plain\">\n<p>It was a breeze to integrate PMPro with the dozens of official and third-party Add Ons. If you need to create a paid LMS (learning management system), PMPro is the one way to go to protect your video contents and provide your users a smooth experience.</p>\n<cite>—Mirco Babini, La Scimmia Yoga Developer</cite></blockquote>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:20%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-thumbnail has-custom-border is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Mirco-Babini-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"Mirco Babini\" class=\"wp-image-513891\" style=\"border-radius:9999px\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Mirco-Babini-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Mirco-Babini-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://www.paidmembers